   ${color8}SWAP:${color7} $swapperc%${color8}${alignr}  
   ${color8}$membar
#${color8}${memgraph 50,150, BEB08D A28E5D -t}${color8}${alignr}  

#${color8}+---------------------------------------------------+
   ${color8}Average CPU: ${color7}$cpu%  ${color8}${alignr}  
